Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,御主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不可以碰到黑泥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的冥界竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么速度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒 你跟藤丸去阻止Beast钻出地面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,包 包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只有两只的话根本不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这个拉赫穆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是新型的「十一个孩子」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,总之我们先牵制住他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好 如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎能让你们得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,得想办法挡下来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这下真的不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这力量 是神灵级吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这句话 之前就想说一次看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此 就拿出看家本领吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说这不符合我的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当年竟然能凭这个让那个阿尔托莉亚上钩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是提亚马特神真正的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每个都足以跟魔神的首领匹敌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 已经能看到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的宝具来绊住她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,玛修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的冥界里 你别想为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast就会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在那里慢慢吞吞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,由本王来助你们一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,从者 Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄王吉尔伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本王看不下去 才会特地来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伽美什王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是从者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他该不会是自力现界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别松懈 不可以分散注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这个反应是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 该不会是固有结界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,世界新生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反创世纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Latina,,0,0,0,,Nega Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Nega Genesis{\r};[英语]对创世纪的否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,天有绝海 地有监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吾之踵乃冥界之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出现吧 发热神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1100,1300,\3c&H81D8FF&\blur15)\fad(0,500)}灵峰踏抱冥界之鞴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1100,1300,\3c&H81D8FF&\blur15)\fad(0,500)}Kur Kigal Irkalla
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,EXComments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Kur Kigal Irkalla{\r}:[苏美尔语]{\rUr3}𒆳  𒆠𒃲  𒅕𒆗𒆷{\r},「山脉之基为冥界」\N在古苏美尔传说中,冥界的入口位于扎格洛斯山脉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,封印Beast了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,内尔伽勒赐予的神殿具现化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.91,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,990)}Nergal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.57,EXComments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Nergal{\r}(内尔伽勒):[苏美尔语]{\rUr3}𒀭𒄊𒀕𒃲{\r}({\rTra}ᵈGIR-UNUG-GAL{\r}),埃列什基伽勒的丈夫.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,确实适合拿来当杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然很不甘心这只能拿来争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个空间肯定还会再尝试用侵蚀逃脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林 反创世纪是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙 打算涂改整个冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,涂改
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,被那个以Beast为核心扩散开来的空间吞噬之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的从者都会被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么不像话的权能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,玛修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟那个不祥的结界对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,必须借用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,某位王思念的白垩之壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要让它显现 或许就能与之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要用玛修的「已然遥远的理想之城」整个撞上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样能抵挡扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在玛修拼命努力的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要有人给Beast最后一击才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 能做到这点的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,反创世纪是否定既有的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,企图诞生出新生命的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 那个空间只能允许生者存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在发动宝具期间她无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个你拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准头部 那里就是弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 在那空间里我的特权就没效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟玛修一起同时使用宝具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为你铺路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,御主 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,玛修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要面向前方使尽全力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,之后的事情就全部交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你 御主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,结界已经快要撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,星之内海 瞭望之台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真名 公开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我立于灾厄之席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从乐园的角落告知汝等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,汝等的故事充满了祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有无罪之人可以进入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是能治愈所有伤痕 所有怨恨的吾等故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,显现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2000,2500,\3c&HF7FF74&\blur15)\fad(0,300}已然遥远的理想之城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.36,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(2000,2500,\3c&HF7FF74&\blur15)\fad(0,300}Lord Camelot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1500,2500,\3c&HE9E3FF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}永世隔绝的理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1500,2500,\3c&HE9E3FF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}Garden of Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Garden of Avalon{\r}:「理想乡的庭院」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,打破冥界的禁忌 出借力量给生者之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了这么多的权能 怎么可能会没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是冥界的女主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了守护冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用了一个 最有可能成功的方法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好不容易才认识了能沟通的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在的你消失了那还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,下次会不会有更戏剧化的 相遇方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟我的基本神性 比现在还要阴沉一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,990)\fs35}性格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可能没办法顺利说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是喜欢现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而是很欣赏那个人类的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的冥界里有那么多花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是一群死者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,由死亡来当你们的对手 也是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受扫荡敌人的委托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你就作为生者向前迈进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都走到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看来分出胜负了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸立香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本王就拿这一击当作饯别礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叙述原初 开天辟地之时 虚无亦为此献上祝贺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以吾之乖离剑撕裂世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,环绕众星之臼 天上的地狱乃创世前夜的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,以你的死来平息一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,2100,\3c&H002BFF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}天地乖离开辟之星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.26,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,2100,\3c&H002BFF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}Enuma Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,孕育了无数的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被无数的生命所敬爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们将我当作阶梯 离我远去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想要爱他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想留在他们身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱 是不是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 孩子们都是爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丢下我离去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再爱我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:23.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏み込んだshadowland 楽園なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 確信なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}それでも go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}しがみつく became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}涙にさえ灯る日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}ひとつのsign ひとつのlight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:47.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}明けない夜も 歌が途切れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:53.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}当てなく迷う夢が縺れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}すれ違った足跡達 振り返らぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏み外したあなたでさえ 手放さないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover I am the prover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:18.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}終らない世界にだって立ち向かうように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:24.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 命の声がまた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}響きだす頃に あなたと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:36.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}沈まずに行く船を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:23.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏入shadow land 才不是乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 无法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.87,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}即使如此 go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}咬紧牙关 became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}连有眼泪都宛如灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}一个sign 一个light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:47.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿没有黎明的夜晚 歌声不会间断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:53.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿不要困在和彷徨迷惑的梦境里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿交错的足迹们不再执着过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿就算你一旦失足 也千万别放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover I am the prover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:18.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但愿能勇敢面对没有结束的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:24.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 生命的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}还在发出声响 与你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:36.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}驶着的船只 不让它沉没
